5. Write a program to convert Decimal number equivalent to Binary number and octal 
numbers? 
Sample Input: 
Decimal Number: 15 
Sample Output: 
Binary Number = 1111 
Octal = 17

CODE: 
public class DecimalConversion {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int decimal = 15;   // change value for testing

        // Convert to binary
        int num = decimal;
        String binary = "";
        while (num > 0) {
            binary = (num % 2) + binary;
            num = num / 2;
        }

        // Convert to octal
        num = decimal;
        String octal = "";
        while (num > 0) {
            octal = (num % 8) + octal;
            num = num / 8;
        }

        System.out.println("Binary Number = " + binary);
        System.out.println("Octal = " + octal);
    }
}
